\begin_inset Formula $P(n)$
\end_inset

 is a proposition that is requires a proof for all 
\begin_inset Formula $n\in\mathbf{I^{+}}$
\end_inset

 or 
\begin_inset Formula $n\in\mathbf{W}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate

\series bold
Basis Step
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
