 for some 
\begin_inset Formula $n=k$
\end_inset

.
 (weak induction)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Assume that 
\begin_inset Formula $P(2)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $P(3)$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $\dotsb$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $P(k)$
\end_inset

 are 
\series bold
True
\series default
 for some 
\begin_inset Formula $n=k$
\end_inset

.
